                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                            <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                <p class="mil-accordion-head">User Experience Enhancements</p>

                                <div class="mil-symbol mil-h3">
                                    <div class="mil-plus">+</div>
                                    <div class="mil-minus">-</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mil-accordion-content">
                                <p class="mil-mb-30">We analyze user feedback and usage data to continually improve the user experience of your app. Our team implements changes and optimizations to keep your users engaged and satisfied with their experience.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                            <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                <p class="mil-accordion-head">App Store Optimization (ASO)</p>

                                <div class="mil-symbol mil-h3">
                                    <div class="mil-plus">+</div>
                                    <div class="mil-minus">-</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mil-accordion-content">
                                <p class="mil-mb-30">We optimize your app for better visibility in app stores, increasing downloads and user engagement. Our ASO service includes keyword research, app description optimization, and regular updates to help your app rank higher and attract more users.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                            <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
